Enum JMadTwissVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<JMadTwissVariable>
      • cern.accsoft.steering.jmad.domain.var.enums.JMadTwissVariable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<JMadTwissVariable>
    public enum JMadTwissVariable
extends java.lang.Enum<JMadTwissVariable>
    This enum groups two MadxTwissVariables together, one for each plane. The correct twiss variable for one plane can then be retrieved through one method.
